data.description: After a detailed renovation, this is the place to call home. Move in Ready 4 bedrooms, 2 bath, 2 car garage with almost 2000 sq ft located in Orange Park. Walk through the inviting foyer and enter into the relaxing family room. Take a tour through the beautiful, upgraded kitchen with California granite countertops and brand new stainless steel appliances. Countertops extend for bar stools. Updated tile in kitchen and bathrooms. Laminate flooring throughout the entire house. No carpet. Journey into the charming master bedroom with 2 walk in closets. Separate vanities on both sides of garden tub in master bath. Walk out onto the wood deck for that weekend barbeque while looking over to the Nature Preserve. Short drive to the mall, restaurants, and great schools.
